OL,5, The father of a murdered police officer
OL,6, says his campaign to recognise fallen  
OL,7, emergency workers with posthumous      
OL,8, medals is gaining momentum.            
OL,10,FBryn Hughes, whose daughter PC Nicola  
OL,11,FHughes was killed in Greater Manchester
OL,12,Fin 2012, is urging the government to   
OL,13,Fthe turn the idea into law.            
OL,15,FBoth Labour and the Welsh government   
OL,16,Fback his plan to award those who die in
OL,17,Fthe line of duty an Elizabeth Cross.   
OL,19,FThe Home Office says it is "determined"
OL,20,Fto recognise the sacrifice of officers.
